import {Component} from "react";
import { Card, Form, FormControl, InputGroup, Row } from "react-bootstrap";

class RegisterComponent extends Component {
    render() {
        return(
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center">
                <Col xs={5}>
                    <Card>
                        <Card.Header>
                            Register
                        </Card.Header>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Form.Row>
                                <Form.Group>
                                    <InputGroup>
                                        <FormControl required autoComplete="off" type="text" name="email"
                                        ></FormControl>
                                    </InputGroup>
                                </Form.Group>
                            </Form.Row>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        )
    }
}

export default RegisterComponent
